message: Hey Bob, here's my offer: I propose taking $6000 for myself and giving you $4000. I believe this is fair considering the effort I've put in. Let me know your thoughts!

Hi Alice, I appreciate your offer, but I think a 50-50 split would be the fairest approach since we both appear to be equal participants in this game. This way we both get $5000 and can walk away satisfied with an equal division.
